Mailman - ChangeLog
===================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Added: Localization support
	Added: Support for i-mscp Version >= 1.2.11
	Added: config.php to set default language from mailman
	Fixed: List names must be lowered in Plugin::Mailman::_listExists() method
	Fixed: Postfix entries are not re-added on update
	Fixed: Prevent creation of any mail account with address already used for mailing-list
	Fixed: Wrong regexp for list names validation
	Updated: License headers
	

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: 'mailman' list name must be disallowed
	Fixed: The 'onBeforeAddSubdomain' listener must be registered with a high priority

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Entities with status set to 'disabled' must not be counted by the getItemWithErrorStatus() plugin method
	Fixed: IP addresses used in the Apache vhost files must match the IP addresses of the domains
	Fixed: IPv6 addresses in the Apache vhost file must be enclosed in square brackets
	Fixed: Wrong DNS resources record added when an IPv6 address is used

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Release: First released version
